Seneca Ave., south side, west from Bryant Ave. to Faile Street. The 3-unit building bears No. 1314 and is known as the Seneca Court. The amaller 4-story building at the S.W. corner of Faile Street bears
No. 868 on the latter.
About 1929.
General Photographic Co.
